page.content: MR EMERY HAS A JEWELLERY STALL.HE LIVES IN BLACKBURN HE HAS HAD A STALL IN GT HARWOOD FOR 2 WEEKS HE HAS OTHER STALLS IN DARWEN,BACUP,AND CLITHEROE.
